          filtering, API integration, or custom filtering logic. This demo shows how to manage
          filtering completely outside the table component with diverse data types and locations. External filtering provides two key benefits: For enum columns with more than 10 options, Simple Table automatically provides a search
          input to help users quickly find and select the desired enum values. This improves
          usability when dealing with large sets of enum options. API Integration: Use

              onFilterChange

